This program will scan the weather and send you a SMS if it is raining. 

Twilio:
Set up a Twilio account
run "pip3 install twilio" in the project directory 

For the app to run without changes, add a "config.py" file to your local repo with the following structure:
weather_api_key = "your api key goes here"
twilio_account_sid = "your twilio sid"
twilio_api_token = "your twilio auth token"
outgoing_number = "number that will receive rain alerts"